### Button (Primary)
  Button (Primary) component
  Props:
    - isDisabled: boolean (optional) — Disable interaction and apply the Figma "Disabled" variant styling.
    - isLoading: boolean (optional) — Replace children with a centered spinner and disable the button.
    - onHover: () => void (optional) — Mouse-enter handler (wraps onMouseEnter for API parity with other DS primitives).
    - icon: React.ReactNode (optional) — Optional leading icon slot (renders before children).

### Button (Outline)
  Button (Outline) component
  Props:
    - isDisabled: boolean (optional) — Disable interaction and apply the Figma "Disabled" variant styling.
    - isLoading: boolean (optional) — Replace children with a centered spinner and disable the button.
    - onHover: () => void (optional) — Mouse-enter handler (wraps onMouseEnter for API parity with other DS primitives).
    - icon: React.ReactNode (optional) — Optional leading icon slot (renders before children).

